title: Health provider contracts (4) with CIGNA Healthcare

communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the New York Freedom of Information Law, I hereby request the following records:

Any and all records related to contracts active as of January 20, 2025 (including but not limited to contracts, exhibits, appendices, legal filings, and any supporting materials) between CIGNA HEALTHCARE and the following 4 health care providers/entities

(1) Dr. Edward Athanasian (individual)
NPI: 1740265727
NY License: 180932

(2) Dr. Edward Athanasian MD PC (organization)
NPI: 1700484052
NY License: 180932
Business address: Hospital for Special Surgery, 535 E 70TH ST, New York, NY, 10021-4823

(3) Legal  name: New York Hospital for the Relief of Ruptured and Crippling…
DBA: Hospital for Special Surgery
NPI: 1598703019
NY License: 7002012H
NY Medicaid: 00243370

(4) HS2, LLC
535 E. 70th St.
New York NY 10021

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 5 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Tracie McMillan

communications.subject: Maryland Public Information Act Request: Maryland State Employees (2022 - 2024)
communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Maryland Public Information Act, I hereby request the following records:

Quarterly electronic listings of all employees of the Maryland Executive Branch from October 1, 2022 through October 1 2024. Specifically, I am seeking electronic listings of all individuals employed within all state agencies, commissions, and departments for each quarter (January, April, July, October) from  October 1, 2022 through October 1 2024.

In particular, I am seeking a spreadsheet with the following fields for each employee: 
- Full legal name (including middle initial)
- Job title
- Department/agency
- Full time/ part time status
- Work street address
- Work zip code
- Hire date
- Gross annual salary
- Civil service status

This is a follow up to a request submitted on December 13, 2022.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 10 calendar days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Ben Goehring
